import Vue from 'vue'
import App from './App.vue'
import router from './router'
import ElementUI from "element-ui";


import "/home/css/bootstrap.min.css"
import "/home/css/owl.carousel.min.css"
import "/home/css/animate.css"
import "/home/css/magnific-popup.css"
import "/home/css/all.min.css"
import "/home/css/flaticon.css"
import "/home/css/themify-icons.css"
import "/home/css/metisMenu.css"
import "/home/css/nice-select.css"
import "/home/css/slick.css"
import "/home/css/main.css"


Vue.config.productionTip = false
Vue.use(ElementUI);

new Vue({
  render: h => h(App),
  router,
}).$mount('#app')
